text: Charles Nicholls (5 December 1901 - 14 January 1983) was an Australian cricketer. He played twelve first-class matches for New South Wales between 1925/26 and 1928/29. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1901 births Category:1983 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers Category:Cricketers from Sydney
